	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi everyone, I'm a new user and i'm also new here. Can i ask anything about NES or SNES repairs or something? I just gotten a SNES which had a screw missing to the 7805 and i added a screw and all is good now. How long will it last with the screw in there? Would the console die without the screw in the 7805?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


